name: The Alphabet Print - personalised
description:
It doesn’t get more simple than the alphabet print. A beautiful way to spell out the initials in a family, a name, word or date. Or keep it simple with just one and personalise with your recipient’s name (seen here). The alphabet print makes for a very unique gift which is personalised with photographs and momentos of your choice. 

Dimensions:
Unframed print			23 x 23cm
Framed print			25 x 25cm 
Depth of frame			4.5cm

What we will need from you:
- The letter(s) or number(s) of your choice (note one letter/number per print)
- At least 10 photographs per print
- Specify if you would like any text on the print (i.e. C is for Chloe)
- Your choice of colour of frame (matt black or matt white)

The team here at The Naughty Little Card Shop would love to hear from you should you have any additional questions or requirements. Just drop us an email at hello@thenaughtylittlecardshop.com

CHEEKY LITTLE TIP:
If you would like to order more than one of the alphabet prints, get in touch with us via email/contact form and we will arrange a discount for you!

Dimensions:
